<A>__{jerry gets out, slams the door, lights a cigarette and walks away. butch waits a few seconds, quietly turns the key one notch and checks the gas ggauge. it reads almost empty. he taps it with his finger but it doesn't budge. he sighs, looks up and sees...}
<B>__{jerry}
<A>__{as he checks one locked car, then feeling eyes on his back, turns, looks at butch, grins and disappears around a corner. butch discreetly exits the car himself, carefully closing the door without a sound.}
